{"tid":1504360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(一句到尾紫絲帶/紅絲帶？）828#metoo追究黑警性暴力集會","createTime":"2019-08-25T09:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T11:49:36.000Z","uid":91221,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"bb58d6dc9f2445deefdf419ea6a588a125a8079a","tid":1504360,"uid":91221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T09:58:14.000Z","msg":"服裝統一都係bloc black，但為咗突顯今次性暴力主題我地可以帶上絲帶🎀響應。另外828集會申請機構平等機會婦女聯盟發起當日用唇膏係手臂寫上#Protesttoo 表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家黎個小投票決定絲帶顏色：<br />\n紫絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n紅絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">紫色 （Ultra violet)</span></strong><br />\n紫色係女權主義代表色，由20年代起各大大少少嘅女性主義遊行、運動都會用呢隻紫色做主題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/boykpCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FboykpCo.jpg&h=c3055263&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDnxfJ3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDnxfJ3.jpg&h=255d3fde&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9RqAJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9RqAJ3.png&h=2dcf4d7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦有唔同有關女性主義著作/電影都以紫色做主題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TFYHCW9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTFYHCW9.jpg&h=4214fe55&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TO4Rg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TO4Rg9.jpg&h=ebd2c0c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2018年Pantone仲選咗呢隻Ultra violet成為2018年度顏色，佢官方指：「除了紀念美國著名歌手Prince之外，更是想<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">通過色彩表達世界各地頻發的性騷擾事件，受害者不再沉默，紫色是反對性暴力事件機構的代表色，暗示着打擊性別歧視及暴力侵害。</span></strong>」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/COWNO4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCOWNO4p.jpg&h=8e7aff65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">最重要係我地用咗呢個有象徵式意義顏色黎做遊行dress code可以draw到國際女權組織或者女權關注者attention，令我地遊行有更多noise！希望引起國際關注香港黑警性暴力對待女示威者問題！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色</span></strong><br />\n有人提議用近期好hit既美劇「使女的故事」著紅衫代女權受到壓迫做主題。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W9GRwix.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW9GRwix.jpg&h=685d2be3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3GFpDz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3GFpDz.png&h=986983e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果做到呢個效果可能好矚目 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PgPWHqf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPgPWHqf.png&h=6d670008&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個人認為統一紫絲帶比較好，因為用返女權運動象徵色會容易spread到msg比國際女權組織，歐洲馬來西亞等各地都曾經以紫色做女性主義、反性暴力theme colour。<br />\n<br />\nPlease vote! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲有人反映#metoo係外國被濫用得太多 雖然申請機構用咗#metoo做集會名 但都討論吓除咗用#protesttoo呢個hashtag之外仲可以用咩tag黎raise awareness?? 又話到比人知係關黑警性暴力對待示威者問題事？ <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aecfeee5a7047e50f788176e75234db58940e42","tid":1504360,"uid":91041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:00:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b74db163d31676aa8cfef62d91514939b874fe1","tid":1504360,"uid":91221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:01:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"554d237b613f4b7a683f8835bb9b0a4e35cafc6d","tid":1504360,"uid":91221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"855cf639db71648a8b92a7f4b37c93f34ae7d8de","tid":1504360,"uid":91221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:01:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"97393136111d73f6d55910627370088b8562c1ed","tid":1504360,"uid":91221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20